Release Notes:
--------
Now greet the arrival of &#039;Sugar Mountain- Live At Canterbury House 1968,&#039;
another singular installment in the continuing Neil Young Archives Performance
Series. On this CD+DVD set, recorded in Ann Arbor, MI, November 9-10, just days
before the release of Young&#039;s self titled solo debut, one of the greatest
singer-songwriters in rock history is heard solo and acoustic at the height of
one of the must tumultuous and creative periods ever experienced both in music
and culture.
